{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_21724.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":1,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story07","chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(*Sigh*... I can't believe I acted so immature@towards a little kid...)","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(Even though I have younger siblings of my own,@just like Tamaki-san does...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(I searched around...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(...but it seems like that girl really did beat@the Witch all by herself...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(She must be strong...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"...[wait:1.0][chara:104301:cheek_0][chara:104301:face_mtn_ex_050.exp3.json][chara:104301:lipSynch_1]Ah."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(Come to think of it, the last train has already@left...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(That's okay. I can just walk another two stations@down.)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(...Maybe I should look for that man from earlier@while I'm at it.)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(It'd be awful if he collapsed somewhere around@here...)"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"[se:7201_detect_magic][chara:104301:effect_ef_adv_01]...?!"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","surround":"7003_wind","textCenter":"(What's this magic power...?@It feels like I'm falling...)","turnEffect":"blackPromist"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(It's...not quite the same as a Witch?@But then...what IS it?!)"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":104301}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnLast":1.5,"bg":"bg_adv_21724.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390101,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"???","textCenter":"...[wait:1.0][chara:390101:lipSynch_1]Oh?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":390101,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Ah... um..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"(Just a girl...? But that's not what that energy@felt like...)"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"id":390101,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"???","surround":"stop","textRight":"Are you a Magical Girl too, by any chance?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":1,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...Uh, are you?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":390101}],"nameRight":"???","textRight":"Yeah? I'm a Magical Girl, just like you."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"(She's gigantic... I wonder how tall she is?)"},{"chara":[{"id":390101,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"???","textRight":"What a coincidence! Were you just out for@a walk?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"I was...yeah, I...guess you could say that?"},{"chara":[{"id":390101,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"You can call me Yuu. What's your name?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...Kuroe..."},{"chara":[{"id":390101}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Kuroe-chan! One second, okay?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":390101,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Let me see... Mm-hm, mm-hm..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":390101}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"You're not on my list, which means you must be@a good person!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_014.exp3.json","id":390101,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Nice to meet you, Kuroe-chan!"},{"chara":[{"id":390101}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"You can call me Yuu. I'm a Magical Girl,@just like you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"(...I'm a little confused, but she...doesn't seem@hostile at all, I don't think?)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":390101,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Oh, um, I've got a quick question."},{"chara":[{"id":390101}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Have you seen any bad guys around here?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":1,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"That's pretty vague..."},{"chara":[{"id":390101,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Uh, well, he's a younger man? And he's bad,@in any case!"},{"chara":[{"id":390101}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"I've got him on my list. Umm... John, that was@his name!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390101,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"I tried to talk to him earlier, right? But then he@took off, so now I'm in a bind."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Uh... I don't know if he's the same guy who ran@by me earlier..."},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"...but I might have seen him."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390101,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Really?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":100,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Yeah. I don't know where he went either,@though..."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"(Was he a bad person?)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390101,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"I see..."},{"chara":[{"id":390101},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"What a pain, what a pain."},{"chara":[{"id":390101}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"John's the last person left on my list..."},{"chara":[{"id":390101}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"...for this area..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390101,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Ah! That reminds me, I'm looking for the Witch's@Labyrinth, too!"},{"chara":[{"id":390101}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"I took out a whole bunch at once..."},{"chara":[{"id":390101}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"...so I've gotta hurry up and get rid of them!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"(...Get rid of what?)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":1,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Well... If you mean the Witch from the station,@I think someone else took care of it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":390101,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Eh?! Is that so? What a pain, what a pain."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":390101,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"But it's a good thing that the Witch is gone now,@huh?"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"motion":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Yeah, that's true."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"(She's kind of weird, but...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"(She seems to be in trouble, so I should help her@out...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"(There's probably a reason...)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"(...why a Magical Girl would be trying to track@down a civilian.)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":1,"motion":200}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Um... I can help you look for that guy you're@after, Yuu-san."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":390101,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Huh, are you sure?!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_014.exp3.json","id":390101}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Thanks a bunch! I'm so happy! Two heads are@better than one, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Yeah..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Then, uh... Let's split up."},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"I'll see if I can find anything around here, and we@can keep in touch through telepathy."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":390101,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Yuu","textRight":"Mm, sounds good."},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Alright, I'll see you in a―"},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"bgEffect":"shakeSmall","chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":390101}],"se":"4061_landing_jump5","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104301,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"Gone already...?! She's fast..."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameLeft":"Kuroe","textLeft":"..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(I'll comb over this area for now...)"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"ef_adv_01","face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":104301}],"se":"7201_detect_magic","textClear":1},{"bgm":"bgm03_story10","chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(A new Witch...?!)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(...No, it's something else. This feels like...@a Doppel...!)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(And...it's coming from the direction of the@station I was at with Nagisa-san...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(It's just one thing after another...@I can't keep up...)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":1}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(...But I don't sense any Witches, so what's with@the Doppel?)"},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(Maybe something is going on...)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":100}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(Tamaki-san would never abandon a fellow@Magical Girl...)"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(I'd prefer it if I didn't have to run into that kid@again, but...)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"..."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":1,"motion":400}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","surround":"7202_telepathy","textCenter":"Excuse me, Yuu-san...!","turnEffect":"ef_adv_02"},{"chara":[{"id":104301}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"I've got some stuff on my mind, so I'm going to@stop looking for that guy for a bit..."},{"chara":[{"id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","surround":"stop","textCenter":"...","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(No response, but I don't have time to wait@for her.)"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":104301,"lipSynch":0,"motion":200}],"nameCenter":"Kuroe","textCenter":"(...Let's go...!)"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
